*.log
/*.py
/*.txt
/*.json
!package.json
.env

# beads compliance audit (separate .git/, hand-built due to swarm DB churn)
/beads_compliance_audit/

# Per-migration backup snapshots of issues.jsonl written by `br migrate`
# (e.g. .beads/issues.jsonl.pre_cvyt0_migration.<ISO8601>.bak). The canonical
# tracked file is .beads/issues.jsonl with no suffix; these timestamped
# .bak siblings are recovery-only and never re-committed.
.beads/issues.jsonl.pre_*.bak
.beads/issues.jsonl.*.bak

# Ephemeral agent/skill scratch (repo-janitor 2026-06-04)
.skill-loop-progress.md
.skill-loop-progress-*.md
*.mcp.json

# === Ephemeral build & scratch artifacts (multi-repo cleanup 2026-06-18) ===
